        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): discover disk compaction checkpoints",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes #68864.\n\n- discover valid `{session}.checkpoint.<uuid>.jsonl` transcript files when `sessions.json` is missing `compactionCheckpoints`\n- include disk-discovered checkpoints in `sessions.list` row count/latest preview and `sessions.compaction.list/get`\n- allow branch/restore to operate on disk-discovered checkpoints, not just metadata-backed checkpoints\n\n## Tests\n\n- `PATH=/tmp/openclaw-corepack-shims:$PATH pnpm check:changed -- --base origin/main`\n- `git diff --check origin/main..HEAD`\n- `node --import tsx -e '<inline script creating a real SessionManager transcript, checkpoint snapshot, then calling listSessionCompactionCheckpointsWithFilesAsync>'`\n- attempted: `corepack pnpm exec vitest run src/gateway/server.sessions.compaction.test.ts -t \"discovers checkpoint transcript files\" --reporter=verbose` (stopped after the local Vitest/Rolldown build stayed in plugin timing output for over two minutes without reaching test assertions)\n- attempted: `corepack pnpm exec vitest run src/gateway/session-compaction-checkpoints.test.ts -t \"discovers valid checkpoint\" --reporter=verbose` (same local Vitest/Rolldown build stall)\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: Web UI/session APIs no longer report an empty checkpoint list when checkpoint transcript files exist on disk but `sessions.json` has no `compactionCheckpoints` metadata.\n\nReal environment tested: Local Linux workspace on this branch with the OpenClaw monorepo at `origin/main` base `3a2220f0a5`.\n\nExact steps or command run after the patch:\n\n```bash\nnode --import tsx -e 'created a real SessionManager session transcript, captured a .checkpoint.<uuid>.jsonl snapshot, omitted compactionCheckpoints metadata, called listSessionCompactionCheckpointsWithFilesAsync, and required one disk checkpoint with matching leaf/sessionFile'\n```\n\nEvidence after fix: Console output from the direct runtime command:\n\n```text\n{\"discovered\":1,\"checkpointId\":\"0f65407f-a898-498e-bcb4-112096da3818\",\"hasLeaf\":true,\"hasSessionFile\":true}\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: The real transcript/checkpoint setup returned exactly one disk-discovered checkpoint and included both the pre-compaction leaf id and snapshot file path.\n\nWhat was not tested: Local Vitest execution did not complete on this host because the test runner stayed in the Rolldown plugin build phase; this PR relies on GitHub CI for actual Vitest execution.\n",
